### Health probes — tüm servisler tek yerde
# Aç → Run all → her servisin durumunu IntelliJ'de canlı gör.
# Ortam değiştirme: sağ-üst dropdown "dev / staging / prod"

# ===== Neurex Web (Next.js) =====
GET {{web}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

# ===== Backend (FastAPI) =====
GET {{backend}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{backend}}/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json

###

# ===== Engine (Flask BDD runner) =====
GET {{engine}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

# ===== Cortex Dashboard (Flask) =====
GET {{cortexDashboard}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

# ===== AI Gateway =====
GET {{aiGateway}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{aiGateway}}/providers/status
X-Internal-Key: {{gatewayInternalKey}}

###

# ===== Observability stack =====
GET {{otelHealth}}/

###

GET {{prometheus}}/-/healthy

###

GET {{tempo}}/ready

###

GET {{loki}}/ready

###

GET {{grafana}}/api/health

###
